has previously stated that he will continue to work on the board of the Ahmed Kathrada Foundation. MPs return to Parliament next week when Ramaphosa will deliver his State of the Nation address. The ANC caucus is also expected to announce who it will nominate as parliamentary committee chairpersons by the end of this week.